title: july 8: it all started in a basement
description:
In this episode of 365 days with mxmtoon, Maia talks about the first issue of the Wall Street Journal in 1889. After, Maia revisits the 1996 release of the Spice Girls debut single, “Wannabe.” Listen to this episode today and make sure you’re following along with the daily updates @365daysmxmtoon on all platforms.
